      "writtenOn": "2021-06-27T15:55:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this should be okay.\n\n24bpp is the framebuffer format and the CPU will convert it to the appropriate data on the bus, either sending 18 bits directly (truncating the low order bits on CPU side) or sending the full 24 bits and the LCD controller will just ignore the low order bits itself.",
